t><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/10/24293054/super-nintendo-world-donkey-kong-country-area-direct-showcase-theme-park" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/10/24293054/super-nintendo-world-donkey-kong-country-area-direct-showcase-theme-park</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-10T14:31:47-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-10T14:31:47-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊测试其杂货业务的混合和匹配</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;纽约州普莱恩维尤的亚马逊生鲜店&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Dt2tsNtt_FaZvoq6cxbFNkl62u0=/187x0:2214x1351/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73713263/2177984001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Howard Schnapp/Newsday RM，来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;N1WVrE&quot;>;亚马逊发展其业务的下一个想法杂货业务可以通过将 Whole Foods 和 Amazon Fresh 两家公司的履行网络融入到一组新的实验中来模糊这两家公司之间的界限，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/articles/amazon-is-looking- to-revamp-its-grocery-delivery-cc0cb57d&quot;>;根据《华尔街日报》&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;P8lDr8&quot;>;据报道，亚马逊已开始从 26 个 Amazon Fresh 配送中心运送 Whole Foods 产品，并计划在宾夕法尼亚州 Whole Foods 市场建立一个微型配送中心，并存放 Amazon Fresh 家居用品和杂货。该计划的另一部分包括一个实验性的“亚马逊杂货店”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/17/24273159/amazon-is-doing-another-grocery-experiment&quot;>;据《华尔街日报》报道，芝加哥全食超市&lt;/a>;提供高档商店通常不会出售的品牌和杂货。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;pP9Dya&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;沃尔玛打赌人工智能可以帮助你更快地购物 - 甚至可能为你购物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/ 9/24032017/walmart-ai-shopping-replenishment-in-home&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊推出无限制杂货配送订阅&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 4/23/24138099/amazon-prime-grocery-subscription-ebt&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;8lGlOH&quot;>;测试的目标是为亚马逊提供客户购买的方式...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/10/24292844/amazon-testing-new-grocery-formats-whole- food-fresh-one-stop-shopping&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/10/24292844/amazon-testing-new-grocery-formats-whole-foods-fresh-one-stop-shopping" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/10/24292844/amazon-testing-new-grocery-formats-whole-foods-fresh-one-stop-shopping</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry></feed>